'''heterophony'''
#The [[simultaneous]] [[performance]], by a number of [[singer]]s or [[musician]]s of two or more [[version]]s of the same [[melody]] or of two or more melodies of differing character.  Frequently, one part [[shadow]]s and [[embellish]]es another part.

